{"tid":2262753,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實分手/被分手嘅人封鎖前任係抱住咩心態居多?","createTime":"2020-10-29T10:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T11:23:07.000Z","uid":208752,"like":47,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0fbff370c1c958ef1dbe833c55db9ff1b8ad7c49","tid":2262753,"uid":208752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"分左手之後, 我一直係度諗緊一個問題。<br />\n情侶分手後, 有啲時候, 總有一方會封鎖咗另一方所有既聯絡渠道。<br />\n通常只有2種情況下會封鎖對方, 小弟想統計一下邊種居多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正皮: 我太痛苦, 太傷心, 所以唔想再見到/聽到一切有關前任既近況嚟勾起回憶<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負皮: who fucking care, 既然分咗手就唔會再接觸, 封鎖又有咩問題? 我只想呢條友永遠咁消失<br />\n<br />\n如果有第3種情況, 歡迎大家係下面留言 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf424323956e40f8b3c2d7bf439269efb17604d","tid":2262753,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:39:45.000Z","msg":"尷尬"},{"pid":"96b11d1b4c5dfc3fa94d591d56e59a2bcc19f00c","tid":2262753,"uid":370062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:40:23.000Z","msg":"怕對方死纏爛打"},{"pid":"a3feed9e1e36c4e78083116b4c33bc22ccad3a2b","tid":2262753,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:41:07.000Z","msg":"If two past lovers remain friends, it's either someone is still in love"},{"pid":"509cc027063aec9a99dae61d87c159282c803f3a","tid":2262753,"uid":288780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:41:50.000Z","msg":"唔想睇到佢 同時知佢係stalker <br />\n間唔時心緒不寧會stalk下自己啲ex<br />\n所以block9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836618b7c1630671c59c7db04f5b3000d1ae8e71","tid":2262753,"uid":208752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:50:22.000Z","msg":"等樓豬分享一下自己嘅體驗,<br />\n我明白分手/被分手嘅痛苦, 所以會選擇封鎖對面, 希望唔會勾起自己嘅情緒, 但樓豬唔會咁做, 因為我比較怕二次傷害到對方, 當A方封鎖咗B方嗰陣, B方必然痛苦, 而A方自己亦都一樣, 只會抵受唔住時不時走去unblock對方, 希望對方注意得到自己 unblock 嘅一刻。<br />\n所以樓豬自己嘅選擇係與其封鎖, 倒不如落得大方。"},{"pid":"cfdee827906a82502753d0f70d3495566bbc6973","tid":2262753,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:51:51.000Z","msg":"分咗手係咪真係需要到block人？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2247393\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2247393</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n追晒佢"},{"pid":"592940c59fb848a4376e6f494ae2d294b32c0bed","tid":2262753,"uid":208752,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3feed9e1e36c4e78083116b4c33bc22ccad3a2b","tid":2262753,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:41:07.000Z","msg":"If two past lovers remain friends, it's either someone is still in love"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:57:00.000Z","msg":"樓豬覺得, 有時兩個人相愛都未必能夠走到最後, 即使分手嗰一刻大家仲係深愛對方<br />\n<br />\n諗多咗兩性嘅關係後, 發覺原來:<br />\n相遇係一種緣分, 相識係一種幸運, 相愛係一種享受，而相伴係一生最大嘅幸福<br />\n<br />\n相愛唔代表兩者都適合, 但能夠搵到適合嘅人相伴一生係每個人所追求嘅目標"},{"pid":"4609c8a99f51239f1b968e97ee043df85d39b23f","tid":2262753,"uid":336565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:58:00.000Z","msg":"想對家打黎搵番自己"},{"pid":"e4f4d25652664c7da82f0eb0807baa805e6c26ac","tid":2262753,"uid":208752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4609c8a99f51239f1b968e97ee043df85d39b23f","tid":2262753,"uid":336565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:58:00.000Z","msg":"想對家打黎搵番自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:03:07.000Z","msg":"見過唔少情況係電話都會Block埋"},{"pid":"983320fba6847b8e9a12e9d61918d219648c428e","tid":2262753,"uid":240150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:10:14.000Z","msg":"Why not both<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87489c07e4796a09deb63960854505